	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SKYSCRAPERS_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Nothing To Lose But Your Chains</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SKYSCRAPERS_HELP">
			<Text>A glorious new dawn awaits comrades! No longer do we have to submit to the corrupt feudal power structures of the past.[NEWLINE]Which bourgeois monument shall we tear down first!?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SKYSCRAPERS_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Invest 5 [ICON_RES_IRON] Iron in building projects such that [ICON_WORKER] Labourers generate +2 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production and +2 [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SKYSCRAPERS_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>All [ICON_GREAT_MERCHANT] Merchants generate -2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold, but all Farms yield +1 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SKYSCRAPERS_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Invest {1_YieldCost} to allow all Farms to yield +1 [ICON_RESERACH] Science.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SKYSCRAPERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>For too long have the peasantry been kept for great works. We will make it so that any man or woman, no matter their birth, can contribute to our nascent paradise!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SKYSCRAPERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>The merchants deal only in death. Their acts bring no real, lasting wealth to our people. Tear them from their hauty offices and send them to the farmland, so that they might learn from whence real wealth is derived.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SKYSCRAPERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>We have cut through the chains of oppression, now we can uplift those who have had opportunity denied to them. Just imagine how much genius has been squandered out in the fields, with no mechanism of recognising scientific gifts.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
